  "reference_number": "GAC0038",
  "remarks": "\nIlko Dimitrov ZHELYAZKOV is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 because there are reasonable grounds to suspect that he is responsible for or has engaged in serious corruption, in the form of bribery, on the basis that he improperly performed a public function in anticipation of accepting an advantage, or in consequence of agreeing to receive an advantage.\n",
